         -------------------------------------------
RESX

                   .--------------------------------
D/CX     ----------&apos;


R/WX     -------------------------------------------

         -------------------------------------------
E

          .--------.   .--------------------------.
D[15:0]/ -| COMMAND|---|  DATA                    |
D[8:0]/   &apos;--------&apos;   &apos;--------------------------&apos;
D[7:0]
</verbatim> Please refer to the MIPI DBI specification for a detailed cycle diagram. </para>
</description>
